snippet.textDisplay: From the release of this song, i was excited to see one of my favourite musicians on board.. Balabhaskar sir, with his violin. Since then the audio has been on my playlist. Since Balabhaskar sir passed away in a tragic accident, i haven't watched the video. Today, something struck me, and I watched it again. I can't control my tears.. i just wish he was still here..
